    "title": "Programme structure",
    "content": "<p><strong>Year One </strong></p>\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"387\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>Code</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"253\">\n<p>Title</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"68\">\n<p>Credits</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>B4XXX</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"253\">\n<p>Critical Issues in International Hospitality</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"68\">\n<p>20</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>BM121</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"253\">\n<p>International Marketing</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"68\">\n<p>20</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>BM131</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"253\">\n<p>Accounting for Managers</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"68\">\n<p>20</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>BMXXX</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"253\">\n<p>Innovation in Hospitality</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"68\">\n<p>20</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>BM137</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"253\">\n<p>Strategic Human Resource Management</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"68\">\n<p>20</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>BMXXX</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"253\">\n<p>Data Analytics and Decision-Making</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"68\">\n<p>20</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>B4XXX</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"253\">\n<p>Hospitality Work Experience</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"68\">\n<p>0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Year Two</strong></p>\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"387\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>Code</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"255\">\n<p>Title</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>Credits</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>BMXXX</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"255\">\n<p>Sustainable Hospitality Operations</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>20</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>BM134</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"255\">\n<p>Strategy and Leadership</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>20</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>BM104</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"255\">\n<p>Research Methods</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>20</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>BM138</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"255\">\n<p>Business Consultancy Project</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"66\">\n<p>60</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
  },
  {
    "key": "9bcdc513-c921-4e38-b51f-b8f5f4e9522b",
    "name": "Key features",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Key features",
    "content": "<p>Placements: A Hospitality Work Experience module is only available and required for those students who are not able to evidence sufficient work experience for entry into the programme. </p>\n<p>Professional registration: n/a</p>\n<p>Any other important points: Applicants without the required one year of work experience may be admitted to the programme. These students will be required to undertake structured, non-credit bearing work experience as part of their first year of the programme.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "8fd3484f-1182-4581-a53a-0b460e92bab2",
    "name": "Admission criteria",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Admission criteria",
    "content": "<p><strong>General Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Successful completion of a Bachelors degree (SCQF 9 or higher) in Hospitality, Hotel Management, Travel, Tourism, Events, Business Administration or cognate disciplines with a minimum average score of 50%</li>\n<li>PLUS at least one year of work experience in a Hospitality related role (this may include hospitality related placements and internships that form part of the applicants degree qualification)*</li>\n</ul>"
  }
]]]></Value>
